{"tid":2302561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想戒酒 可以點搞","createTime":"2020-11-27T08:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T09:15:07.000Z","uid":146934,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9095f57b1ab9955a0fc24c0abc406853ecc0bbe","tid":2302561,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:18:56.000Z","msg":"自從呢一兩年比以前飲多好多酒<br />\n我覺得個人身體差咗<br />\n轉數慢咗<br />\n記性差咗<br />\n濕疹勁咗<br />\n洗費多咗<br />\n胃痛多咗<br />\n啤酒肚大咗<br />\n心情差咗<br />\n<br />\n每日最少飲兩罐啤酒/whiskey起跳<br />\n有時出街食飯會飲<br />\n冇得飲就會匿埋喺房自己飲<br />\n開心會飲 唔開心會飲得更多<br />\n好撚鐘意wing wing地嘅感覺<br />\n好想飲醉但飲極都唔醉<br />\n然後第二朝起身就會後悔點解飲咁多<br />\n好頭痛<br />\n個人會好抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n但試過唔飲一兩日就會失眠 就好想飲<br />\n試過飲無酒精嗰類 好難飲好大浸麥味<br />\n有冇過來人分享下點戒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想未到三十歳就變到佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1SvCtN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1SvCtN.jpg&h=bcd4ccea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0969d727965fcceb6c347d2c7f5b6208170bcbde","tid":2302561,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:25:35.000Z","msg":"首先試下慢慢咁飲少D<br />\n例如平時3罐既話 咁就試下2罐<br />\n習慣左就1罐<br />\n<br />\n我都介緊"},{"pid":"def1a56e21a1c866767ea9809c8ff08fda7aff86","tid":2302561,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"同埋我之前都試過唔飲會失眠 捱過頭2,3就OK<br />\nP.S. 之前1日2,3罐, 而家1星期1,2日 先飲2,3罐"},{"pid":"134f988bd2cc41e5ec0e7604a949b34940fa9a7e","tid":2302561,"uid":19172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"同你一樣好鐘意飲<br />\n<br />\n但有做gym 同帶氧 所以冇咩問題"},{"pid":"40c328beb0fdc5a1456ad7b4c3f0e217e0f49d69","tid":2302561,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0969d727965fcceb6c347d2c7f5b6208170bcbde","tid":2302561,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:25:35.000Z","msg":"首先試下慢慢咁飲少D<br />\n例如平時3罐既話 咁就試下2罐<br />\n習慣左就1罐<br />\n<br />\n我都介緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"同自己講飲一罐<br />\n之後就會追酒飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9499c88529693dcd7bd2d8400f48e19f676c92a2","tid":2302561,"uid":25387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:13:44.000Z","msg":"我都係wo 我想界開個喉嚨直接倒d酒精落個胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2460c7977c785534688a30a31906f77247305b8e","tid":2302561,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"飲生命之水"}]}